values:
Life's pretty empty lately.&nbsp;

It's like that moment while waiting for the page on internet explorer to load. Especially if you have a slow connection, it can be somewhat irritating.

I'm blank.
I'm waiting.

I'm on cough syrup for a cold.
I'm on vitamins for malnutrition.
I'm on sleep medication so I'm not always awake.

And this dead end.

I've hit it before, but it's still pretty difficult to get out of, don't you think?
So if I cry alot, does that mean my smile is genuine?

Mall tomorrow.&nbsp;
Civies on Thursday.&nbsp;
Movies&nbsp;on Friday.&nbsp;
Party on Saturday.&nbsp;
Friend's house on Sunday.
